    %% S2-UC2..6 attach to SPA_MAIN/SPA_CLIENT, not to each other. ---
    SPA_CLIENT["src/app/src/api/client.js — SPA API ADAPTER (S2-UC1; +getFlow s004-UC1; +getStagingQueue DEF-012)<br/>only module knowing :3001 base URL + endpoint shapes<br/>getActive/getProjects/getQueues/getPolicy/getBaseline/getFlow/getStageFlow/getStagingQueue/subscribeEvents<br/>fail-soft: null on net/HTTP/parse error"]:::def012changed
