    SPA_FLOWPARSER["src/app/src/parsers/flow.js — flow.md time-thief + queue parser (s004, domain)<br/>parseFlow(raw)->{timeThieves,queues,sourceRef}; raw-string fidelity (§8 F3)<br/>picks tables by header cell; fail-soft → empty arrays, no throw"]:::delivered

